{
  "stem": "6719.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, uh, as I was saying before, uh, I-- I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And not only that, uh, you know, in Austria, there was always anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if anybody made any remarks to me, like, dirty Jew, which was very-- you know, [NON-ENGLISH], and I'm not going to spell that because that is really insignificant.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it used to be [NON-ENGLISH] this and [NON-ENGLISH], which means, uh, uh, pigs-- uh, pigs-- uh, pig's Jew-- pig Jew, or something like that, if-- if you can translate it literally.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knocked his brains out, and I had a lot of fights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And nobody-- although my mother always said, don't fight, you know, you're going to get hurt, I-- I didn't take this-- this was-- this was taboo as far as I'm concerned.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, uh but other than that, I got along very well with almost everybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Public-- for four years in a public school, then I went to, uh, what they called the junior high school, which was also public.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there were two divisions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You either went to the gymnasium, which was privately owned, and-- and you had to pay for your tuition down there, uh, uh, or you went to the public school system as such, which usually started at six, from the time you were six years old till you were 14.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's it, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that I would say it's about, oh, 20%, 25%.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uh, there were a lot of Jewish kids down there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an integrated area.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Uh, see, the, uh-- the, uh-- the area we lived in, which was the 20th district, was adjacent to the 2nd district.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the 2nd district was 90% Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's where Jews-- most of the Jews lived down there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
